good privacy browsers:
- Bromite, Bromite SystemWebView
- Ungoogled Chromium

browser which are better than Google Chrome:
- Brave Private Browser, Brave Browser (Beta), Brave Browser (Nightly)
- Kiwi Browser Next
- Vivaldi

and:
- Firefox Lockwise

